From 116870217ede9fde57faf91cca4e6fa1adf3279f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Yuvasree Sivasankaran <ysivasan@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 29 Sep 2025 10:39:51 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:DP:wifi:ath12k: Add global debugfs knob for dp stats

Add global debugfs knob for enabling different dp stats
via debug mask for each stats. Also add single debugfs knob
to reset dp, debug_dp and ext tx and rx stats.

Command to enable below stats
1. Enable_dp_stats
echo 0x1 > /sys/kernel/debug/ieee80211/phy00/dp_stats_mask
2. Enable_dp_debug_stats
echo 0x2 > /sys/kernel/debug/ieee80211/phy00/dp_stats_mask
3. Ext_tx_stats
echo 0x4 > /sys/kernel/debug/ieee80211/phy00/dp_stats_mask
4. Ext_rx_stats
echo 0x8 > /sys/kernel/debug/ieee80211/phy00/dp_stats_mask
5. Tid stats
echo 0x10 > /sys/kernel/debug/ieee80211/phy00/dp_stats_mask
6. Enable all stats
echo 0x1F > /sys/kernel/debug/ieee80211/phy00/dp_stats_mask

Command to reset dp, debug dp and ext tx and rx stats
echo 1 > /sys/kernel/debug/ieee80211/phy00/reset_dp_stats

Signed-off-by: Yuvasree Sivasankaran <ysivasan@qti.qualcomm.com>
